item.title: 🙋‍♂️ About Me
item.description: Hello, I'm Yuechen Zhu 👋 I am a passionate and creative software engineer with a strong background in developing innovative software solutions. My journey in the world of technology began at a young age when I discovered my love for coding. Since then, I have honed my skills and expertise to become a proficient developer. My Expertise I specialize in building robust and scalable web applications using modern technologies such as JavaScript, React, and Node.
